%% Diagram: QPACK Required Insert Count blocks one stream, not all
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Enc as Encoder
    participant Req as Request stream
    participant Dec as Decoder

    Enc->>Dec: Insert "x-custom" (encoder stream) → table[62]
    Enc->>Req: Header block, RIC = 63

    Note over Req,Dec: Request arrives before insert
    Note over Dec: RIC 63 > current 62 → block this stream only

    Note over Enc,Dec: Encoder-stream insert reaches Dec
    Note over Dec: count = 63 → unblock request stream

    Dec-->>Enc: Section Acknowledgment (decoder stream)
